---
title: Easy Sichuan Garlic Beef Strip Tacos with Pickled Onion
description: If you like bold flavours and Asian cuisines, you’ll love food from the Sichuan province in China! We’ve dialled down the chilli but kept the tasty garlic and umami flavours for an easy-to-eat taco that will appeal to everyone.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sichuan-garlic-beef-tacos-51e46b11.jpg
